UID:40SuzBo4-dNb9TYxYXgQO
SUMMARY:Albers Graduate Information Session
DTSTAMP:20260409T031209Z
DTSTART:20260416T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Interested in a graduate program at Albers? Have questions abou
	t the admissions process? Want to connect with a current student or facult
	y member from your program of interest?\n\n \n\nOur online information ses
	sions provide more insight into your desired program and answer any questi
	ons you may have. Join us at one of our events to learn more! During our g
	raduate information sessions we take a deep dive into the following progra
	ms offered by the Albers School of Business and Economics:\n\n \n\nEarly C
	areer MBAProfessional MBA \\(in-person program only\\)Sport and Entertainm
	ent Management MBAMaster of Professional Accounting \\(STEM\, for non-acco
	unting majors\\)Master of Science in Accounting & Analytics \\(STEM\, for 
	accounting majors\\)Master of Science in Business Analytics \\(in-person p
	rogram only\\) \\(STEM\\)Master of Science in Finance \\(STEM\\) \n\nWe pr
	ovide detailed information such as program structure\, prerequisites\, app
	lication information\, admissions processes\, scholarships\, and more.\n\n
	 \n\nTo participate with video\, you will need access to a device with a c
	amera \\(laptop\, smart phone\, etc.\\). A Zoom account is not required. Y
	ou may also choose to participate through audio only.\n\n \n\nAlbers has s
	eparate recruiting events for the following:\n\nOnline: MBA\, MSBA\, Cyber
	security Leadership programs\n\nLeadership Executive programs including th
	e MBA and Certificate \n\n \n\nPlease email albersgradinfo@seattleu.edu fo
	r more information.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/alber
	s-graduate-information-session/16656682/2026-04-16T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - A
	ll Events
