UID:cW7GqfrXRct6q85Mkxqb6
SUMMARY:1980s sing along
DTSTAMP:20260409T031209Z
DTSTART:20260417T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Central District (1.9 miles E)\n\nThe Totally ‘80s Sing Along p
	rojects 30 music videos with subtitles on screen so you can sing along to 
	Madonna\, Prince\, Michael Jackson\, Billy Idol\, George Michael\, Depeche
	 Mode\, Whitney Houston\, and David Bowie at Central Cinema\, 1411 21st Av
	e. in Seattle. To buy a $17 ticket\, click “8:00” on their page\, and then
	 “Continue As Guest.”\n\nhttps://central-cinema.com/movie/totally-80s-sing
	-along/\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
