	R 6 Tools\, when you log in to your MIC \\(Member Information Center\\). M
	aximize Your Membership 101 workshop is designed to educate our valued mem
	bers on the benefits of using your Chamber Master access. We will also cov
	er networking opportunities and advocacy that are available to you as a me
	mber of the Renton Chamber of Commerce. This training session will equip y
	ou with the ability to navigate and utilize your MIC Tools to effectively 
	promote your business reaching over 10k potential customers. Posting Jobs\
	, Events\, Member 2 Member and Hot Deals\, and more\, will be shown. MYM i
	s an essential to for new members onboarding and current members who need 
	a refresher course\, who want MAXimize Your Membership!  Our membership is
	 similar to a gym... the more you use it\, the better the results!  We als
	o welcome businesses who are interested in chamber membership to join us! 
