UID:2usupeNr-j0su8X3VA86_
SUMMARY:RANU - Renton Area Nonprofits Unite
DTSTAMP:20260409T031211Z
DTSTART:20260422T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:RANU \\(Renton Area Nonprofits Unite\\) is for any nonprofit in
	 or benefiting the greater Renton area.  An opportunity for like-minded or
	ganizations to network and connect and build bridges. Each meeting has a s
	ubject matter presentation designed to uplift those working in the nonprof
	it world. January Topic: Every Fourth Wednesday of the Month 9:00 - 10:30 
	AM  FREE Physical & Verbal De-Escalation  Presenter: Sharon Bebop of 3E Be
	havioral Solutions will be presenting on physical and verbal de-escalation
	. Feel free to invite colleagues!!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/
	#/details/ranu-renton-area-nonprofits-unite/18408099/2026-04-22T00\n\nFrom
